bicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012906, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "May the Almighty accept all your ziyarats. May He make them the best treasure for the Hereafter. May He allow for the intercession of Ahle Bayt (a) from the time of our death till Paradise and even in Paradise, at every step. And may He award us a place in their proximity in Paradise. Ameen.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Khuda-wande Aalam aap ki tamaam ziyarato’n ko qabool farmaaye. Isko roz-e-aakherat ke liye behtareen zakhira qaraar de. Maut ki manzil se qayaamat tak aur qayaamat mein bhi ham sab ko har qadam par Ahlebait (a) ki shafa’at naseeb kare aur Jannat mein unke qareeb jagah inaayat farmaaye, Aameen.", "UrduDescription": "خدا وندے کریم آپ کی تمام زیارتوں کو قبل فرمائے۔ اس کو روزِ آخرت کے لیئے بہترین ذخیرۂ قرار دے، موت کی منزل سے قیامت تک اور قیامت میں بھی ہم سب کو ہر قدم پر اہلِ بیتؑ کی شفاعت نصیب فرمائے اور جنت میں ان کے قریب جگہ عنایت فرمائے، آمین۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": 